*Vladislavs Kozlovs (born 1987), footballer
*Žanis Peiners (born 1990), basketball player
*Gunta Vaičule (born 1995), sprinter

==Climate==
Rēzekne has a humid continental climate (Köppen &quot;Dfb&quot;).
==Twin towns – sister cities==

Rēzekne is twinned with:
* Arendal, Norway
* Braslaw, Belarus
* Częstochowa, Poland 
* Krychaw, Belarus
* Sianów, Poland
* Soroca, Moldova
* Utena, Lithuania
* Vitebsk, Belarus
