==Sister cities==
Burnaby has four sister cities:
* Kushiro, Hokkaido, Japan (1965)
* Mesa, Arizona, United States (1998)
* Hwaseong, Gyeonggi-do, South Korea (2010)
* Zhongshan, Guangdong, China (2011)

